{"tid":1758625,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"月至今用約萬枚催淚彈　11.12中大及多區衝突單日最多佔兩成","createTime":"2019-11-27T07:17:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T07:25:08.000Z","uid":333488,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3bc38b6a11e5d2132988c9dc756e9f15298b86a3","tid":1758625,"uid":333488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T07:17:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5VcVOG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5VcVOG.jpg&h=35a293b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自今年6月爆發反修例風波以來，示威衝突不斷。據警方統計，本港6月至今有超過900宗示威，警方共使用了約10,000枚催淚彈，包括手擲式及催淚煙子彈。<br />\n<br />\n其中單日使用最多催淚彈的日數，首位是11月12日的三罷行動，警方在港島、沙田、荃灣、將軍澳、天水圍、屯門，初步點算共使用2,330枚催淚彈，即佔五個月來使用催淚彈總數至少兩成。當日的焦點是中大二號橋的衝突。<br />\n<br />\n其次是10月1日國慶日的全港各區衝突，以及11月18日理大及油尖旺的衝突，以及8月5日三罷的各區衝突，分別涉及1,667枚、1,458枚、1,002枚催淚彈。<br />\n<br />\n真係痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d09cadb641d58d5d1fa450d397001648c3030be","tid":1758625,"uid":47223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T07:20:08.000Z","msg":"二噁英 山埃毒害唔會即刻顯現 慢性謀殺香港人"},{"pid":"2b597c68b9043c602b3a53736313050e57ae950b","tid":1758625,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T07:21:28.000Z","msg":"要大力文宣，等藍絲都屌popo"},{"pid":"72d9b213ed20f89450b9bd5b290c0bc57ead73e9","tid":1758625,"uid":333488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T07:23:28.000Z","msg":"其實想知破咗世界紀錄未"},{"pid":"72f7b210549dd43347c4bf94fa3edc566d55d911","tid":1758625,"uid":59633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72d9b213ed20f89450b9bd5b290c0bc57ead73e9","tid":1758625,"uid":333488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T07:23:28.000Z","msg":"其實想知破咗世界紀錄未"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T07:25:08.000Z","msg":"有排都未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif